title: The Simpsons Take a Dig at NFTs, Crypto in 'Treehouse of Horror' Episode
description: "Remember how we were always saying we wish Bart was less fungible," Homer asks Marge after he puts his son on-chain.

title: SEC Clashes With Do Kwon and Terraform Labs in Court, Alleging ‘Clear, Undisputed’ Fraud
description: Last week, lawyers representing Terraform Labs and its ex-CEO Do Hyeong Kwon (Do Kwon) moved to dismiss the lawsuit brought against them by the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC). In response, the SEC has countered with a motion of its own, asserting the accountability of both the company and Kwon. The commission maintains that […]
